### ğŸ¯ Challenge
**Build and Print a Linked List**
```python
class Node:
    def __init__(self, data):
        self.data = data
        self.next = None
```

#### ğŸ” Example
```mermaid
graph LR
    10 --> 20 --> 30 --> 40
```

<details>
<summary><b>âš¡ Pro Tip</b></summary>

Use dummy nodes to simplify edge cases:
```python
dummy = Node(0)
current = dummy
for num in [10,20,30]:
    current.next = Node(num)
    current = current.next
```
</details>

